            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "@kylesower:\n\n> This sounds like it may be two issues?\n\nYes, two very different symptoms. But both are terminal-related issues introduced by 0.12.0. I suspect some terminal-related logic problem that manifests itself in different ways depending upon the ssh client.\n\nFWIW, prompted by the fact that Neovim 0.11.6 on my Fedora box didn’t manifest either of these two issues, I tested a few older versions of Neovim for macOS, and it looks like both of these terminal-related issues were introduced in the 0.11.7 → 0.12.0 transition, and persist as of 0.13.0. So, for the time being, falling back to 0.11.7 avoids both of the issues in these two iPadOS ssh clients.",
